'''&quot;Garden of Bones&quot;''' is the fourth episode of the [[Season 2|second season]] of ''[[Game of Thrones]]''. It is the fourteenth episode of the series overall. It premiered on April 22, 2012. It was written by co-executive producer [[Vanessa Taylor]] and directed by [[David Petrarca]].

The episode won a [[wikipedia:Creative Arts Emmy Award|Creative Arts Emmy Award]] for Art Direction in a Single-Camera Series in September 2012&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.westeros.org/GoT/News/Entry/Game_of_Thrones_Wins_Big_at_Creative_Arts_Emmys/ Westeros.org]&lt;/ref&gt;.

